snippet.title: DID I LIST 100 THINGS? Reseller Vlog + WHAT SOLD + Help Me Spend My Reselling Profits on Stocks!
snippet.description:
@Amber Resells and I set out on a challenge to see how much profit we could earn from reselling in a 9 day period. What would we do with our profits? Invest in the stock market! We're both pretty new to the stock market, so we thought it would be fun to see if we could make our profit make us more money! This vlog / what sold video has it all - reselling tips on topics like reseller inventory storage, crosslisting, and more - as well as a record of every item I sold throughout the week on reselling platforms like Poshmark, eBay, and Tradesy. Make sure you check out Amber's video!
